author: Josh Feldman
title: CNN’s Toobin: Is Devin Nunes ‘Clueless or Corrupt or Both’?
text:
CNN’s Toobin: Is Devin Nunes ‘Clueless or Corrupt or Both’? by Josh Feldman | 8:21   
CNN’s Jeffrey Toobin went off on House Intel Committee Chairman Devin Nunes tonight following the New York Times report that two White House officials helped provide him with the intel reports he read on White House grounds. 
Nunes said earlier this week in a CNN interview, “I’m quite sure that people in the West Wing had no idea I was there.” 
Toobin was stunned by some of the language the chairman of the House Intelligence Committee was using to talk about being on White House grounds: 
This guy is so far out of his depth, he has no idea what he’s doing. The question about whether he’s clueless or corrupt or both is really the only question left in this investigation, at least as far as he’s concerned. 
Watch above, via CNN.
